href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jqf1665702735257.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqf1665702735257.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqf1665702735257.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jqf1665702735257\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      U4 upgrade\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Drop and create all tables and procedures.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__topic_d60053e1_d60054e1_d60055e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__p_d60056e1_d60057e1_d60058e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= U4 upgrade</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__section_c55_qww_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d356727e63\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__p_d60062e1_d60063e1_d60064e1\">This option is used for data type migration, and\n            enables you to migrate a database that does not support numerics to a database that\n            supports numerics.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__p_d60065e1_d60066e1_d60067e1\">When this option is enabled, the Create Table facility\n            generates SQL commands that drop and recreate all tables and procedures. Therefore, the\n            database objects can be upgraded to the SYB U4.0 connector.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__note_syx_qww_jcc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The data in the tables must be exported before the\n            upgrade scripts are executed. Otherwise, all data will be lost when the tables are\n            dropped by the SQL script.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__p_d60068e1_d60069e1_d60070e1\">When the Create Script utility creates the enforce\n            referential integrity constraints in your DBMS scripts, it builds SQL to drop SYB U2.x\n            and U3.x triggers and to create SYB U4.x or U5.x referential integrity controls.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__p_d60071e1_d60072e1_d60073e1\">You do not need this option if you are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__ul_tyx_qww_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__li_d26687e1_d26688e1_d26689e1\">Migrating from a database that already provides\n               numeric support </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqf1665702735257__li_d26690e1_d26691e1_d26692e1\">Migrating from a \"disable numerics\" environment,\n               and you plan to use the <code class=\"ph codeph\">disable numerics</code> connector option. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528994\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528994\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "U4 upgrade Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 U4 upgrade Drop and create all tables and procedures. USYS$SYB_PARAMS = U4 upgrade Description This option is used for data type migration, and enables you to migrate a database that does not support numerics to a database that supports numerics. When this option is enabled, the Create Table facility generates SQL commands that drop and recreate all tables and procedures. Therefore, the database objects can be upgraded to the SYB U4.0 connector. Note: The data in the tables must be exported before the upgrade scripts are executed. Otherwise, all data will be lost when the tables are dropped by the SQL script. When the Create Script utility creates the enforce referential integrity constraints in your DBMS scripts, it builds SQL to drop SYB U2.x and U3.x triggers and to create SYB U4.x or U5.x referential integrity controls. You do not need this option if you are: Migrating from a database that already provides numeric support Migrating from a \"disable numerics\" environment, and you plan to use the disable numerics connector option. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}